<i>adverb</i>: 확고히 [확꼬히], 억척같이 [억척까치], 결연히 [겨련히], 결단코 [결딴코] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>확고히 [확꼬히]</dt><br>
<dd>firmly; determinedly; unshakably</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 상황 등이 확실하고 굳세게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's attitude or situation, etc., being clear and unchanging.</dd><br>
<dt>억척같이 [억척까치]</dt><br>
<dd>toughly; determinedly; relentlessly</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 억세고 끈덕지게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very rough and persistent manner.</dd><br>
<dt>결연히 [겨련히]</dt><br>
<dd>resolutely; determinedly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 확고한 마음가짐과 태도로.</dd><br>
<dd>With a very resolute mind and attitude.</dd><br>
<dt>결단코 [결딴코]</dt><br>
<dd>1. by all means; determinedly</dd><br>
<dd>어떠한 경우에도 반드시.</dd><br>
<dd>By all means, under any circumstances.</dd><br>
<dd>2. never; by no means</dd><br>
<dd>어떠한 경우에도 절대로.</dd><br>
<dd>Never in any case.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>